<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sarah K. – Portfolio</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Syne+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f0e8;
            color: #1a1814;
            font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* --- NAV --- */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #c8bfad;
        }

        nav .logo {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #4a4540;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            gap: 28px;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav a {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #4a4540;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #8b5e3c;
        }

        /* --- HERO --- */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background-color: #ede6d6;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #c8bfad;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        }

        .hero h1 em {
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #4a4540;
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        }

        .hero-label {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #8b5e3c;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* image placeholder */
        .hero-photo {
            width: 200px;
            height: 260px;
            background-color: #c8bfad;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* --- TAGS --- */
        .tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .tag {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #c8bfad;
            color: #4a4540;
        }

        /* --- PROJECTS --- */
        .projects {
            padding: 60px 40px;
        }

        .projects h2 {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #4a4540;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .project-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .card {
            flex: 1;
            border: 1px solid #c8bfad;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 160px;
            background-color: #ddd4bc;
        }

        /* different placeholder colors per card */
        .card:nth-child(2) .card-image { background-color: #c8c8bc; }
        .card:nth-child(3) .card-image { background-color: #b8b0a0; }

        /* number badge using position */
        .card-num {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            background-color: #f5f0e8;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            color: #1a1814;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-type {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: #8b5e3c;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: #4a4540;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* --- ABOUT --- */
        .about {
            display: flex;
            background-color: #1a1814;
            color: #f5f0e8;
            border-top: 1px solid #c8bfad;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-right: 1px solid #3a3530;
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text h2 em {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #c8ad8a;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #a09880;
            max-width: 380px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .about-list {
            width: 280px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .about-list p {
            border-top: 1px solid #3a3530;
            padding-top: 14px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .about-list .year {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: #8b5e3c;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .about-list .place {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #605850;
            display: block;
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #c8bfad;
        }

        footer p {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #4a4540;
            margin: 0;
        }

        footer ul {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        footer a {
            font-family: 'Syne Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #4a4540;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #8b5e3c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <span class="logo">sasokru.github.io</span>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#">Work</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div>
            <p class="hero-label">Portfolio · Hamburg 2025</p>
            <h1>Sarah<br><em>Kruschinski</em></h1>
            <p>Nursing meets code. I study Business Informatics &amp; Digital Media at Leuphana and work as a nurse at UKE — interested in where healthcare and technology overlap.</p>
            <div class="tags">
                <span class="tag">Digital Health</span>
                <span class="tag">Web Dev</span>
                <span class="tag">Data Viz</span>
                <span class="tag">UX</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-photo"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="projects">
        <h2>Selected Work</h2>
        <div class="project-grid">

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <span class="card-num">01</span>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-type">Web · Seminar</p>
                    <h3>This Portfolio</h3>
                    <p>Built with HTML &amp; CSS from scratch for the Web Programming seminar at Leuphana.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <span class="card-num">02</span>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-type">Data · Internship</p>
                    <h3>Editorial Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Power BI dashboard tracking content performance across digital channels at stern+.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <span class="card-num">03</span>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-type">Research · Health</p>
                    <h3>Heuristics in the ED</h3>
                    <p>Seminar paper on clinical decision-making and micro-certainty in emergency settings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
        <div class="about-text">
            <h2>Nurse by night,<br><em>developer</em> by degree.</h2>
            <p>I'm drawn to systems — whether that's a triage protocol or a data pipeline. Exploring where clinical knowledge and software design can build something genuinely useful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-list">
            <p>
                <span class="year">2023 – now</span>
                Nurse · UKE Hamburg
                <span class="place">Universitätsklinikum</span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="year">2023 – now</span>
                B.Sc. Business Informatics
                <span class="place">Leuphana University</span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="year">2024</span>
                Digital Strategy Intern
                <span class="place">Stern+, Hamburg</span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="year">2027 (planned)</span>
                Semester Abroad
                <span class="place">HKBU, Hong Kong</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 Sarah Kruschinski</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/sasokru">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">LinkedIn</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Mail</a></li>
        </ul>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
